text: Jeanine Emelie Marcelle Touchard-Vapaille (25 November 1924 - 23 December 2005) was a French gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all- around at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1924 births Category:2005 deaths Category:French female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics
